parameters:
...Oh? Are you a girl I haven't seen around here before?
Could it be...

Um, I'm a traveler. I'm on my way to visit Ise Shrine... Is
this an inn?

Oh, a traveler, are you? Welcome to the wooden lodging of
Suranamu Village! It's only 10 mon to stay, will you be
lodging with us?
Eh? 10 mon!? Is it really that cheap?

Yes. It's very dangerous to camp outside in this village
with such poor public order. After all, bandits have their
base nearby...

There are many kidnappers, and it's the most dangerous place
in Kanto. It's unthinkable for a woman to sleep outside. I
recommend you stay at this inn. Fufufu...
(What should I do... Should I stay at this inn...)
Stay at the wooden lodging \c[27][H Event]\c[0]
木賃宿に泊まる\c[27]【Ｈイベント】\c[0]

That's right. Then, I'll take care of myself here for one
night.

Ho-ho! Thank you very much! Then please come this way~ We'll
also prepare some ochazuke for a late-night snack.
You serve dinner too? That's great\I[15]I love ochazuke!
--The innkeeper led Karin inside the inn.
...I'm sorry. I'll have to decline this time.

Oh! Are you staying with us again!? You're more than
welcome!

No, I'm heading back... (This inn is dangerous. It's still
better to camp outside...)
